WEBVTT

00:03.642 --> 00:05.245
Could you please turn that down?

00:08.335 --> 00:12.229
Oh yeah, could you please bring the water glasses from the lazy susan?

00:15.470 --> 00:17.843
Could you please wait here for a moment?

00:23.036 --> 00:24.405
Would you please hold me?

00:27.519 --> 00:30.291
Winston, would you please put out that cigarette?

00:33.231 --> 00:36.150
Would you please tell Mr. Cooper that I'm here?

00:41.609 --> 00:43.757
Would you mind bringing the drinks menu?

00:47.519 --> 00:49.742
Would you mind telling me what all this is about?

00:55.785 --> 00:58.355
Please don't call me. Please.

01:01.595 --> 01:03.563
Please don't be late for dinner in the future.

